{"tid":886725,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【代理裁員潮】中原年底炒500人 4成來自新界區","createTime":"2018-11-02T10:13:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T14:31:23.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bd3ebe533cf38809c826c6f4919acc7ce8e43074","tid":886725,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T10:13:44.000Z","msg":"樓市不穩下，代理開單困難，部份佣金不達標的代理有機會年底被解僱。市場近日流傳中原西半山區開始裁員，中原地產亞太區副主席兼住宅部總裁陳永傑表示，該傳聞並不屬實，因為西半山長期賺錢，經營容易，租金不算貴，屬中原銷量最top的區域，要裁應該係新界區。因為新界區有1,600個員工，而西半山只有200人。<br />\n<br />\n陳永傑表示，如果該批代理於今年1至12月只得10萬佣金，集團將嚴格執行Quota制度，即每月平均低於6.8萬元佣金將會被裁走。年底時會邀請每月不足一萬佣金的代理先行離職，約500人，當中包括200名全年零佣金的代理，預計其中有4成代理來自新界區。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181102&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58867580\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181102%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58867580&d=%2FwvC0QD7q%2Bc%2B2coBXKGRyTANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=66c1fa7e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181102%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58867580&h=a0d504e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181102&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58867580</a>"},{"pid":"e7fcb9c6ff135663e590ecb8b3f3c13e6d51b34f","tid":886725,"uid":32114,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T10:32:05.000Z","msg":"年底時會<span style=\"color: red;\">邀請</span>每月不足一萬佣金的代理先行<span style=\"color: red;\">離職</span><br />\n邀請離職咁有禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n地產狗應邀失業<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"567a2c010dde9af38d0d33fa34fd261bdf7f831b","tid":886725,"uid":32114,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e7fcb9c6ff135663e590ecb8b3f3c13e6d51b34f","tid":886725,"uid":32114,"like":3,"dislike":0,"sc